title: [Feymist Cemetery, Mire]
description: Cracked and weathered tombstones litter the area, most of which are crooked and sinking into the wet ground.  A grove of large moss-covered yews circles the mire, blocking much of the moonnlight.  Somewhat sunken, a headless cracked marble sculpture stands near a shattered headstone.
